						"title": "Talk to our storage team",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "Schedule a call with our team to explore Cloudflare's globally distributed data and storage solutions and optimize your current stack for performance, cost, and scale.\n\n- __Optimize your data stack__. Discover how to build more resilient, cost efficient, and faster applications by connecting Cloudflare's full suite of data and storage products. We'll show you how to get the most out of your architecture.\n- __Customize your demo__. Get a live walkthrough of products like __R2__ for zero-egress object storage, D1 for serverless SQL, and __Workers KV__ for low-latency key-value storage, all tailored to your specific use case.\n- __Learn about pricing and migration__. Receive a complete analysis of your current setup, a transparent pricing breakdown, and a step-by-step strategy for seamless migration to Cloudflare.\n\n---\n\nDue to our team's limited bandwidth, \nrequests are subject to an approval process.",
